        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 22 at 5:08PM PDT until August 22 at 5:30PM PDT by NWS Las Vegas NV</headline>
        <description>At 508 PM PDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 8 miles northeast of
Daggett, moving north at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and blowing dust.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Daggett and Newberry Springs.

This includes the following roads...
Interstate 15 in California between mile markers 82 and 98.
Interstate 40 in California between mile markers 8 and 24.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
